{"tid":1458511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【行動檢討】今日有去機場嘅麻煩入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T18:43:49.000Z","uid":140738,"like":64,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"c74e1e42eeb8c3a68b631a7234d0358af21b0e8b","tid":1458511,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:15:23.000Z","msg":"今日算係好成功咁令大量飛機起唔到飛，<br />\n<br />\n行動好成功，大家唔好互屌，<br />\n<br />\n比啲掌聲自己先。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有樣野一定要講，<br />\n<br />\n大約五點至六點嗰陣，<br />\n<br />\nArrival hall係亂到走難咁，<br />\n<br />\n消息不斷傳黎傳去，<br />\n<br />\n大家都唔知邊樣真邊樣假。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家收到消息想傳比附近嘅人知<br />\n<br />\n唔緊要，盡量唔好叫出黎，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日有人舉牌講消息，<br />\n<br />\n係一個唔錯嘅方式，</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為你係現場收到嘅消息，<br />\n<br />\n其實大部分人都會收到，<br />\n<br />\n唔太需要大叫，<br />\n<br />\n令現場更混亂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，<br />\n<br />\n入機場嘅另一個目標係要宣傳警察暴行比班遊客聽，<br />\n<br />\n但今日咁嘅情況，<br />\n<br />\n係完全宣傳唔到，<br />\n<br />\n做唔到今次行動嘅最大效果，<br />\n<br />\n我見班鬼佬鬼婆完全無心機留意啲文宣，<br />\n<br />\n個個淨係表現得有啲驚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結<br />\n<br />\n機場本身就係一個唔多需要緊張嘅地方，<br />\n<br />\n我地去接機同食飯其實唔犯法，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而且和你飛原意就係想宣傳比啲遊客睇</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最重要係<br />\n<br />\n麻煩唔好無啦啦大叫<br />\n<br />\n有消息嘗試用舉牌方式同人講<br />\n<br />\n緊張氣氛係會互相傳染<br />\n<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"0766a268d30347c261237325eca2fc401e4499f3","tid":1458511,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805e7480f119afdd28f55cd1acf2f46907508f69","tid":1458511,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68148aae14c578340c302d90cb4f5b764b62b50a","tid":1458511,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:16:37.000Z","msg":"推出國際"},{"pid":"449c64a3a3ff06af3b06503ef62bcaf91fd2912a","tid":1458511,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92e041684642628c2f88221bfd636874178891d","tid":1458511,"uid":38768,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:18:46.000Z","msg":"溫柔同善意 係必要<br />\n今日都有好幾位外國人比個微笑同 like 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我做既只係舉牌同對住佢微笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea8c3862d62cb8d2a1a78d9029038215a298d533","tid":1458511,"uid":231342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:19:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1457735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1457735</a><br />\n呢個post咪講咗囉"},{"pid":"7c25e07c1842f31f1d1f1355a086e3ac77ec22f6","tid":1458511,"uid":31320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:19:40.000Z","msg":"[是日戰績] 半日政府損失 二千五百萬財務業績<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1458428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1458428</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔好再塞鐵塞路<br />\n低效率高風險<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港，得一個國際機場<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n緊記：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有旅客就去，冇旅客就退</span></span>"},{"pid":"2e012c1ead86054dc3e724cdd01279550de60ac9","tid":1458511,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"q